<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3606780>
    dc:description "Figs. 30-34. Head of Oenopiella species, in dorsal view. (30) O. unidentata. (31) O. punctaria. (32) O. pallidula. (33) O. flonensis, holotype. (34) O. ventanensis, holotype. c, clypeus; mp, mandibular plates. Scale bars = 1 mm. (Online figure in color.)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3606780/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3606772>
    dc:description "Figs. 1-5. Dorsal view of species of Oenopiella. (1) O. unidentata. (2) O. punctaria. (3) O. pallidula. (4) O. flonensis, holotype. (5) O. ventanensis, holotype. Scale bars = 1 mm. (Online figure in color.)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3606772/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3606782>
    dc:description "Figs. 35-46. Pygophores of Oenopiella species. (35-37) O. unidentata, in (35) dorsal, (36) posterior, and (37) ventral views.(38-40) O.punctaria, in (38) dorsal,(39) posterior, and (40) ventral views.(41-43) O.flonensis, holotype, in (41)dorsal, (42) posterior, and (43) ventral views. (44-46) O. ventanensis, holotype, in (44) dorsal, (45) posterior,and (46) ventral views. Scale bars = 1 mm. (Online figure in color.)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3606782/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3606788>
    dc:description "Figs. 57-62. Paramere and phallus of O. punctaria. (57-59) Right paramere in (57) dorsal, (58) outer side, and (59) inner side views. (60-62) Phallus in (60) lateral, (61) ventral, and (62) dorsal views. aa, articulatory apparatus; dc, dorsal connectives; dsd, ductus seminis distalis; er, ejaculatory reservoir; pab, base of paramere; pah, head of paramere; pc, processus capitati; ph, phallotheca; prph, processus phallothecae; pv, processus vesicae; sg, secondary gonopore. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3606788/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3606790>
    dc:description "Figs. 63-66. External and internal female genitalia of Oenopiella species. (63) O. unidentata. (64) O. punctaria. (65) O. pallidula. (66) Internal genitalia of O. punctaria. aaf, anterior annular flange;ch, chitinellipsen; cs, capsula seminalis; dr, ductus receptaculi; g9, gonapophysis 9; gc8, gonocoxite 8; gc9, gonocoxite 9; la8, laterotergite 8; la9, laterotergite 9; or, orificium receptaculli; paf, posterior annular flange; pi, pars intermedialis; sp, spiracle; tvi, thickening of vaginal intima; va, vesicular area; X, tenth segment. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3606790/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3606784>
    dc:description "Figs. 47-50. Line drawings of Oenopiella species' pygophores in posterior view. (47) O. unidentata. (48) O. punctaria. (49) O. flonensis, holotype.(50) O.ventanensis, holotype.pa, paramere;vr,ventral rim of pygophore;X,tenthabdominalsegment.Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3606784/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3606786>
    dc:description "Figs. 51-56. Dissected pygophores of Oenopiella species. (51-53) O. unidentata in (51) posterior, (52) dorsal, and (53) ventral views. (54-56) O. punctaria in (54) posterior, (55) dorsal, and (56) ventral views. Scale bars = 1 mm. (Online figure in color.)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3606786/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

